quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,1,"By those who range themselves in rows;"
  37,2,"by those who reprove severely,"
  37,3,"and those who recite the Exhortation;",footnotes:180690:1
  37,4,"surely your God is One,",footnotes:180691:1
  37,5,"the Lord of the heavens and the earth and of whatever lies between the two, the Lord of the Easts.",footnotes:180692:1,footnotes:180693:2
  37,6,"We have adorned the lower heaven with the adornment of the stars",footnotes:180694:1
  37,7,"and have protected it from every rebellious satan.",footnotes:180695:1
  37,8,"These satans cannot listen to what transpires in the High Council for they are pelted away from every side"
  37,9,"and are repelled. Theirs is an unceasing chastisement."
  37,10,"And if any is able to snatch a fragment, he is pursued by a piercing flame.",footnotes:180696:1